					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Given a frame of 192 displayable scanlines on the master system, leaving 70 for vblank, what's the total number of bytes the z80 can write to the VDP? And what method does it use? I've seen the number of ~900bytes being throw around, but I thought TmEE said it could be higher than that.</div>

					
